<TEXT>
<P>
 I'm writing to let you know that I (unlike Mary Lou Quirt from Thousand Oaks) 
enjoyed your article on how to boil an egg (In the Kitchen, Aug. 11). I am a 
wife and full-time mother of two children, and must say I'm a pretty good 
cook.One of my biggest problems has always been how to boil a perfect egg -- 
especially one that doesn't have the shell stuck to it. After reading your 
article, I have found success. I've even placed the "recipe" on the inside of 
my cupboard! 
</P>
