<P>
 Sheriff's deputies have released a composite drawing to help snare an armed 
robber who also allegedly sexually assaulted two Camarillo teen-agers. 
According to witness accounts, the rapist is a white male 18 to 23 years old; 6 
feet, 1 inch tall; who weighs about 200 pounds and was wearing a long-sleeved 
green shirt, dark baggy trousers and black combat boots. 
</P>
<P>
 The manhunt, directed by Sgt. John Fitzgerald of the Ventura County Sheriff's 
Department, included 20 to 30 law officers who were to canvass the Camarillo 
area Wednesday night. 
</P>
