<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFLY; VOLUNTEERS: MEALS DRIVERS NEEDED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A local Meals on Wheels program needs help delivering meals to homebound 
people. 
</P>
<P>
 The Santa Monica/Malibu Meals on Wheels seeks volunteers to deliver hot noon 
meals and cold evening meals to as many as 14 people between 11 a.m. and 1 
p.m., Monday through Friday. 
</P>
<P>
 Because of a shortage of volunteer drivers, the program is placing those 
requesting the service on a waiting list, often for up to three weeks. 
Information: (310) 394-7558. 
</P>
