<TEXT>
<P>
 A 5-year-old central Los Angeles boy found his jailed father's pistol 
Wednesday and fired the weapon twice, hitting the ground with the first shot 
and fatally wounding his 1 1/2-year-old brother with the second, Los Angeles 
police said. 
</P>
