<P>
 Cereal Maker Tinkers With the 'Classics': Minneapolis-based General Mills 
Inc., second only to Kellogg Co. in the ready-to-eat cereals market, has new 
recipes for its top-selling Cheerios and "Breakfast of Champions" Wheaties. The 
