<TEXT>
<P>
 Housing Permits: Through July this year, Orange County developers took out 
8,466 new-housing permits, compared to 3,809 permits for the first seven months 
of 1993, according to the Construction Industry Research Board, a trade group 
in Burbank.  
</P>
