<P>
 The Vaqueros made a great playoff run after finishing third in league and they 
should be back for more. Frank (1,956 yards, 21 TDs) figures to be one of the 
county's top quarterbacks. Allen might be the area's most electrifying player. 
But Young, a transfer from Edison, will get most of the carries and Allen could 
play more flanker than tailback. "Young's a quick learner and an exceptional 
athlete," Case said. "He fits right into my type of scheme." The Vaqueros' 
weaknesses are the offensive line and overall depth. SCHEDULE 
